name: Founder Bets Master SPV LLC
description: Developer of a mobile application designed to create a consumer experience for discovering real estate. The company's application combines property and neighborhood data with an engaging full-screen video feed to explore properties, enabling customers to browse video listings of homes and neighborhoods.
